text: Ahmed Dini Ahmed (1932 - 12 September 2004) was a Djiboutian politician. He was the second Prime Minister of Djibouti from 1977 to 1978. Dini Ahmed died on 12 September 2004 at a French military hospital in Djibouti City.Cherif Ouazani, "Ahmed Dini Ahmed", Jeuneafrique.com, September 19, 2004 . ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Prime ministers of Djibouti
